{"version":1,"entries":{"person_4647809_translations":{"at":1772469925791,"data":{"id":4647809,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Trey Lindsay","primary":true}}]}},"person_5342543_translations":{"at":1772469939846,"data":{"id":5342543,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Emilija Matić","primary":true}}]}},"person_5196630_translations":{"at":1772469945689,"data":{"id":5196630,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"จิ๊ อัจฉราพรรณ ไพบูลย์สุวรรณ","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Atcharaphan Phaibunsuwan","primary":false}}]}},"person_11367_translations":{"at":1772469952904,"data":{"id":11367,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Bradley Whitford (born October 10, 1959) is an American actor and producer. He is best known for his portrayal of White House Deputy Chief of Staff Josh Lyman in the NBC television political drama The West Wing (1999–2006), for which he was nominated for three consecutive Primetime Emmy Awards from 2001 to 2003, winning in 2001. The role earned him three consecutive Golden Globe Award nominations.\n\nIn addition to The West Wing, Whitford played Danny Tripp in Studio 60 on the Sunset Strip, Dan Stark in the Fox police buddy-comedy The Good Guys, Timothy Carter, a character who was believed to be Red John, in the CBS series The Mentalist, antagonist Eric Gordon in the film Billy Madison, Arthur Parsons in The Post, Dean Armitage in the horror film Get Out, Roger Peralta in Brooklyn Nine-Nine, President Gray in the dystopian science fiction film The Darkest Mindsand Rick Stanton in the monster film Godzilla: King of the Monsters.\n\nIn 2015, he won a second Primetime Emmy Award for his role as Marcy in Transparent and later garnered a fifth nomination for portraying Magnus Hirschfeld in the same series. Since 2018, Whitford has portrayed Commander Joseph Lawrence in the Hulu dystopian drama The Handmaid's Tale, for which he won his third Primetime Emmy Award in 2019.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Bradley Whitford, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Bradley Whitford","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"布莱德利·惠特福德（Bradley Whitford，1959年10月10日-），美国影视演员。他最出名的角色是在 NBC 电视剧《西翼》中饰演白宫副幕僚长乔什·莱曼、在日落大道 60 号工作室中饰演丹尼·特里普、在福克斯警匪喜剧《好家伙》中饰演丹·斯塔克、在 CBS 系列剧《心理医生》中饰演雷德·约翰，以及在电影《比利·麦迪逊》中饰演反派埃里克·戈登。\n\n2001 年至 2003 年，惠特福德因在《西翼》中的角色而连续三次获得艾美奖“剧情类剧集杰出男配角”提名，并于 2001 年获得该奖项。这个角色也为他赢得了连续三次金球奖“最佳男配角”提名。","name":"布莱德利·惠特福德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"브래드리 휘트포드","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"布萊德利·惠特福德（Bradley Whitford，1959 年 10 月 10 日-），美國影視演員。他最出名的角色是在 NBC 電視劇《西翼》中飾演白宮副幕僚長喬什·萊曼、在日落大道 60 號工作室中飾演丹尼·特里普、在福克斯警匪喜劇《盜亦有道》中飾演丹·斯塔克、在 CBS 系列劇《心理醫生》中飾演雷德·約翰，以及在電影《比利·麥迪遜》中飾演反派埃里克·戈登。\n\n2001 年至 2003 年，惠特福德因在《西翼》中的角色而聯續三次獲得艾美獎“劇情類劇集傑出男配角”提名，並於 2001 年獲得該獎項。這個角色也為他贏得了聯續三次金球獎“最佳男配角”提名。","name":"布萊德利·惠特福德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Брэдли Уитфорд","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Бредлі Вітфорд","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"בראדלי וויטפורד","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1575535_keywords":{"at":1772469955370,"data":{"id":1575535,"keywords":[]}},"person_1853548_translations":{"at":1772469959507,"data":{"id":1853548,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"张幽舞 配音导演，知名ACG歌姬，同时也是一名资深的主持人。声线清甜温柔，同时也擅长活泼正太型角色，对于角色的情感状态把握极其优秀，所演绎的角色极具生命力。除此之外还是多场重量级ACG演唱会、活动的主持与评委。2020年4月起，加入三格声米工作室。","name":"张幽舞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhang Youwu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhang Youwu","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжан Ю У","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"張幽舞 配音導演，知名 ACG 歌姬，同時也是一名資深的主持人。聲線清甜温柔，同時也擅長活潑正太型角色，對於角色的情感狀態把握極其優秀，所演繹的角色極具生命力。除此之外還是多場重量級 ACG 演唱會、活動的主持與評委。2020 年 4 月起，加入三格聲米工作室。","name":"張幽舞","primary":false}}]}},"person_4297031_translations":{"at":1772469966278,"data":{"id":4297031,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Aditya Nanda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"Aditya Nanda","primary":true}}]}},"person_5823_translations":{"at":1772469968278,"data":{"id":5823,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Dame Julia Elizabeth Andrews, DBE (born Julia Elizabeth Wells; 1 October 1935) is a British film and stage actress, singer, and author. She is the recipient of Golden Globe, Emmy, Grammy, BAFTA, People's Choice Award, Theatre World Award, Screen Actors Guild and Academy Award honours. Andrews was a former British child actress and singer who made her Broadway debut in 1954 with The Boy Friend, and rose to prominence starring in other musicals such as My Fair Lady and Camelot, and in musical films such as Mary Poppins (1964), for which she won the Academy Award for Best Actress, and The Sound of Music (1965): the roles for which she is still best-known. Her voice, which originally spanned four octaves, was damaged by a throat operation in 1997.\n\nAndrews had a revival of her film career in 2000s in family films such as The Princess Diaries (2001), its sequel The Princess Diaries 2: Royal Engagement (2004), the Shrek animated films (2004–2010), and Despicable Me (2010). In 2003 Andrews revisited her first Broadway success, this time as a stage director, with a revival of The Boy Friend at the Bay Street Theatre, Sag Harbor, New York (and later at the Goodspeed Opera House, in East Haddam, Connecticut in 2005).\n\nAndrews is also an author of children's books, and in 2008 published an autobiography, Home: A Memoir of My Early Years.","name":"Julie Andrews","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"줄리 앤드류스","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Dame Julia Elizabeth Andrews (DBE), mais conhecida como Julie Andrews,  é uma atriz, cantora e escritora britânica em cinema e teatro. Ela recebeu os prêmios Globo de Ouro, Emmy, Grammy, BAFTA, People's Choice Award, Theatre World Award, Screen Actors Guild e Academy Award.\n\nJulie foi atriz e cantora infantil na Inglaterra e estreou na Broadway em 1954 com The Boy Friend, e ganhou destaque estrelando outros musicais na Broadway  como My Fair Lady e Camelot e filmes musicais em Hollywood como Mary Poppins (1964), com o qual ganhou o Oscar de Melhor Atriz e A Noviça Rebelde (1965): papéis pelos quais ela ainda é mais conhecida. Sua voz, que originalmente media quatro oitavas, foi danificada por uma operação na garganta em 1997.\n\nJulie teve um renascimento de sua carreira cinematográfica nos anos 2000 em filmes de família, como O Diário da Princesa (2001), sua sequência O Diário da Princesa 2: Casamento Real (2004), Shrek (2004-2010) e Meu Malvado Favorito (2010). Em 2003, Julie revisitou seu primeiro sucesso na Broadway, desta vez como diretora de teatro, com uma remontagem de The Boy Friend no Bay Street Theatre, Sag Harbor, Nova York (e posteriormente na Goodspeed Opera House, em East Haddam, Connecticut, em 2005 )\n\nJulie também é autora de livros infantis e, em 2008, publicou uma autobiografia, Home: A Memoir of My Early Years.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Dame Julie Elizabeth Andrews, DBE; bürgerlich Julie Andrews Edwards (* 1. Oktober 1935 als Julia Elizabeth Wells in Walton-on-Thames), ist eine britische Schauspielerin, Sängerin, Schriftstellerin und Synchronsprecherin. Internationale Bekanntheit erlangte sie in den 1960er Jahren als Musicaldarstellerin, vor allem durch ihre Hauptrollen in den Filmmusicals Mary Poppins und Meine Lieder – meine Träume. Daneben gab sie zahlreiche Konzerte auf der ganzen Welt, bis sie 1997 infolge einer misslungenen Operation ihre Gesangsstimme verlor. Danach widmete sich die Oscar-Preisträgerin vermehrt dem Schreiben; besonders erfolgreich war sie als Autorin von Kinderbüchern.\n\nQuelle: Wikipedia","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"ca","name":"Català","english_name":"Catalan","data":{"biography":"Dame Julie Elizabeth Andrews, nascuda Julia Elizabeth Wells, DBE (Walton-on-Thames, Surrey, Anglaterra, 1 d'octubre de 1935)[2] és una cantautora i actriu de teatre i cinema anglesa. Ha estat guardonada amb el Globus d'Or i els Premis Emmy, Grammy, BAFTA, People's Choice, Theatre World, Screen Actors Guild i Oscar. Andrews va ser una actriu i cantant infantil que va debutar a Broadway el 1954 amb The Boy Friend, i que va saltar a l'estrellat en musicals com My Fair Lady i Camelot; i al cinema en pel·lícules com Mary Poppins (1964) i Somriures i llàgrimes (1965), els papers pels que és més coneguda. La seva veu de soprano arribava a quatre octaves, fins que li va ser malmesa en una operació de laringe el 1998.\n\nAndrews va tenir un revival a la seva carrera als 2000, en pel·lícules familiars com The Princess Diaries (2001), i la seva seqüela The Princess Diaries 2: Royal Engagement (2004); així com la saga d'animació Shrek (2004-2007). El 2003 revisità el seu primer èxit de Broadway en dirigir The Boy Friend al Bay Street Theatre, Sag Harbor, New York.\n\nJulie Andrews també és una autora de llibres infantils, i el 2008 va publicar una autobiografia.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朱莉·安德鲁斯女爵士DBE（英语：Dame Julie Andrews，原名：茱莉亚·伊丽莎白·威尔士Julia Elizabeth Wells； 1935年10月1日－）是英国女演员、歌手和作家。她曾获奥斯卡金像奖、英国电影学院奖、艾美奖、金球奖、格莱美奖、美国演员工会奖、全美民选奖和世界戏剧奖。她在音乐剧《窈窕淑女》的演出令她的知名度急升，《欢乐满人间》和《音乐之声》两套电影演是她的代表作。\n\n朱莉·安德鲁斯在2008年出版自传《Home: A Memoir of My Early Years（家：我早年的一部回忆录）》。","name":"朱莉·安德鲁斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Julie Andrews est une actrice, chanteuse et écrivaine britannique, née le 1er octobre 1935 à Walton-on-Thames dans le Surrey.\n\nEnfant de la balle, Julie Andrews débute sur scène à l'âge de douze ans et conquiert Broadway, en 1954, avec The Boy Friend, une comédie musicale importée d'Angleterre. Chanteuse et actrice reconnue, elle doit cependant laisser à Audrey Hepburn le soin d'incarner à l'écran le rôle principal de My Fair Lady, qu'elle avait fait triompher sur scène. Le destin lui sourit pourtant très vite lorsqu'en 1964, elle débute sur grand écran en tenant le rôle-titre de Mary Poppins, qui lui apporte la gloire et l'Oscar de la Meilleure actrice. Ironie du sort, elle décroche cette récompense alors même qu'Audrey Hepburn est elle-même nommée pour My Fair Lady.\n\nJulie Andrews enchaîne alors les comédies musicales, remportant notamment un triomphe avec La Mélodie du bonheur de Robert Wise. Elle aborde également d'autres registres tels le drame Hawai de George Roy Hill ou le thriller Le Rideau dechire, qui la fait jouer sous les ordres d'Alfred Hitchcock.\n\nSa carrière prend une nouvelle impulsion lorsqu'elle rencontre son futur mari, le réalisateur Blake Edwards, qui lui donne quelques-uns de ses rôles les plus marquants. Une féminité plus agressive et davantage d'ambiguité caractérisent alors ses personnages dans des films comme Top Secret ou Elle, et surtout le double rôle de Victor Victoria. Après une prestation remarquée dans un autre film de son mari, That's life, où elle incarne une femme mûre atteinte d'un cancer, Julie Andrews délaisse le cinéma au profit de la télévision pendant une quinzaine d'années.\n\nC'est avec une production signée Disney, Princesse malgré elle, tournée sous la direction de Garry Marshall et dans lequel elle incarne la Reine de Génovie, qu'elle fait son grand retour au cinéma en 2001. Trois ans plus tard et après avoir prété sa voix à une autre Reine, celle de Shrek 2, elle accepte de reprendre son rôle dans une suite intitulée Un mariage de princesse. Elle ne quitte pas le monde de l'animation puisqu'elle joue dans les suites de Shrek, ainsi que dans Il était une fois, mêlant film et dessin animé. Inépuisable, elle prête sa voix à la mère de Gru, le héros de Moi, moche et méchant (2010).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"茱莉·安德魯絲","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジュリー・アンドリュース","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"جولي آندروز","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Τζούλι Άντριους","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"ג׳ולי אנדרוז","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"जूली ऐंड्रूज़","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джули Эндрюс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джулі Ендрюс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"จูลี แอนดรูว์","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"茱莉·安德絲女爵士 DBE（英語：Dame Julie Andrews，原名：茱莉亞·伊利沙伯·威爾士 Julia Elizabeth Wells； 1935 年 10 月 1 日－）是英國女演員、歌手和作家。她曾獲奧斯卡金像獎、英國電影學院獎、艾美獎、金球獎、格林美獎、美國演員工會獎、全美民選獎和世界戲劇獎。她在音樂劇《窈窕淑女》的演出令她的知名度急升，《歡樂滿人間》和《艷尼歌聲》兩套電影演是她的代表作。\n\n茱莉·安德絲在 2008 年出版自傳《Home: A Memoir of My Early Years》。","name":"茱莉·安德絲","primary":false}}]}},"person_4366430_translations":{"at":1772469970047,"data":{"id":4366430,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Pin Danita Choktadaporn is a singer, actress and member of the girl group Cosmos and the sub-unit Comsos Sun under Star Hunter Entertainment (สตาร์ ฮันเตอร์ เอ็นเตอร์เทนเม้นท์). After graduating from Nawaminthrachinuthit School, she went on to study at Chulalongkorn University's Faculty of Veterinary Science.","name":"Danita Choktadaporn","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"Pin Danita Choktadaporn","primary":true}}]}},"person_